election_record.label: Vermont 1817 Council

overview.note: The Original Election Returns list 13457 votes for Joel Doolittle, 13410 votes for David Fay, 13368 votes for Frederick Bliss, 13230 votes for Daniel Peaslee, 13131 votes for Ezra Butler, 13221 votes for William Cahoon, 13120 votes for Truman Chittenden, 13219 for Theophilus Crawford, 13196 votes for Pliney Smith, 13186 for Timothy Stanley, 13165 votes for Thomas Hammond, 12980 votes for Elias Keyes, 7423 for Denison Smith, 7414 votes for Moses Robinson, 7396 votes for Gamaliel Painter, 7362 votes for Nathaniel Chipman, 7357 votes for John W. Chandler, 7354 votes for Asa Lyon, 7352 votes for Royal Corbin, 7319 votes for Jedediah P. Buckingham, 7319 votes for Zadock Wheeler and 7249 votes for Zerah Willoby and 7220 votes for Jonas Mann.

The Rutland Vermont Herald (Rutland, VT), The Northern Sentinel (Burlington, VT), The National Standard (Middlebury, VT) and North Star (Danville, VT) report 13457 votes for Joel Doolittle, 13410 votes for David Fay, 13368 votes for Frederick Bliss, 13430 votes for Daniel Peaslee, 13131 votes for Ezra Butler, 13221 votes for William Cahoon, 13120 votes for Truman Chittenden, 13219 for Theophilus Crawford, 13196 votes for Pliney Smith, 13186 for Timothy Stanley, 13165 votes for Thomas Hammond, 12980 votes for Elias Keyes, 7423 for Denison Smith, 7414 votes for Moses Robinson, 7396 votes for Gamaliel Painter, 7362 votes for Nathaniel Chipman, 7357 votes for John W. Chandler, 7354 votes for Asa Lyon, 7352 votes for Royal Corbin, 7319 votes for Jedediah P. Buckingham, 7319 votes for Zadock Wheeler and 7249 votes for Zerah Willoby and 7220 votes for Jonas Mann.

Spooner's Vermont Journal (Windsor, VT) reports 13457 votes for Joel Doolittle, 13410 votes for David Fay, 13368 votes for Frederick Bliss, 13430 votes for Daniel Peaslee, 13131 votes for Ezra Butler, 13221 votes for William Cahoon, 13120 votes for Truman Chittenden, 13219 for Theophilus Crawford, 13196 votes for Pliney Smith, 13186 for Timothy Stanley, 13165 votes for Thomas Hammond, 12980 votes for Elias Keyes, 7423 for Denison Smith, 7414 votes for Moses Robinson, 7396 votes for Gamaliel Painter, 7362 votes for Nathaniel Chipman, 7157 votes for John W. Chandler, 7354 votes for Asa Lyon, 7352 votes for Royal Corbin, 7319 votes for Jedediah P. Buckingham, 7319 votes for Zadock Wheeler and 7249 votes for Zerah Willoby and 7220 votes for Jonas Mann.

The Vermont Intelligencer, and Bellows Falls Advertiser (Bellows Falls, VT) reports 13457 votes for Joel Doolittle, 13410 votes for David Fay, 13368 votes for Frederick Bliss, 13430 votes for Daniel Peaslee, 13131 votes for Ezra Butler, 13221 votes for William Cahoon, 13120 votes for Truman Chittenden, 13219 for Theophilus Crawford, 13196 votes for Pliney Smith, 13186 for Timothy Stanley, 13107 votes for Thomas Hammond, 12980 votes for Elias Keyes, 7424 for Denison Smith, 7641 votes for Moses Robinson, 7399 votes for Gamaliel Painter, 7362 votes for Nathaniel Chipman, 7357 votes for John W. Chandler, 7354 votes for Asa Lyon, 7352 votes for Royal Corbin, 7319 votes for Jedediah P. Buckingham, 7319 votes for Zadock Wheeler and 7246 votes for Zerah Willoby and 7220 votes for Jonas Mann.

"The highest on the republican ticket for Council (Mr. Doolittle) has 13,457--the highest on the federal (Mr. Smith) 7423--the lowest stand 12,980 to 7,220--average plurality 5,883." Vermont Gazette (Bennington, VT). October 28, 1817.

sub_unit.name: Chittenden
sub_unit.note: Three votes for Ezra Butler listed in the Original Election Returns as scattering have been added to his county total.
